"Charles ""Chic"" Sale" https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_%22Chic%22_Sale 0 Charles Partlow "Chic" Sale (August 25, 1885 – November 7, 1936) was an American actor and vaudevillian. He was a son of Frank and Lillie Belle (née Partlow) Sale, and the brother of actress/writer Virginia Sale-Wren.
